IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: To foster youth athletics, primarily in the sport of rowing, for students of loyola academy
IRS990.MissionDesc: LOYOLA ACADEMY ROWING ASSOCIATION WAS ESTABLISHED TO PROVIDE AN OPPORTUNITY TO LOYOLA ACADEMY STUDENTS TO LEARN THE CHALLENGE OF ESTABLISHING A GOAL AND ACHIEVING THE DESIRED RESULTS THROUGH THE CHALLENGE OF ROWING.
IRS990.Desc: To teach the technique, skill and style of rowing and apply the lessons to the races entered. To appreciate the necessity of team effort and practice sportsmanship and fairplay throughout the season in the boats and elsewhere.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION A LINE 7A
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION HAS MEMBERS WHO HAVE THE POWER TO ELECT OR APPOINT ONE OR MORE MEMBERS OF THE GOVERNING BODY.

BOARD MEMBERS RECEIVE AN ELECTRONIC COPY OF FORM 990 PRIOR TO FILING. THE INDEPENDENT CPA HIRED TO PREPARE FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND INFORMATION IS AVAIBABLE TO ADDRESS QUESTIONS OR CONCERNS PRIOR TO FILING

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 12
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE BOARD HAS ADOPTED A CONFLICT-OF-INTEREST POLICY WITH DISCLOSURE STATEMENT. EACH BOARD MEMBER MUST COMPLETE OR UPDATE ANNUALLY THE DISCLOSURE STATEMENT. ALL ARE REVIEWED ANNUALLY BY THE BOARD.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 15
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION HAS NO EMPLOYEES HOWEVER THE BOARD REVIEWS ANNUALLY THE COMPENSATION OF COACHES BASED ON PERFORMANCE EVALUATION IN CONNECTION WITH ESTABLISHED GOALS AND OBJECTIVES, AND DETERMINES COMPENSATION REASONABLENESS THEREOF AND BY REVIEWING DATA FOR SIMILAR ORGANIZATIONS.
THE ORGANIZATION MANAGEMENT PROVIDES UPON REQUEST INFORMATION SUBJECT TO PUBLIC DISCLOSURE. ADDITIONALLY, THE THREE MOST RECENT YEARS OF FORM 990 BY THE ORGANIZATION ARE AVAILABLE AT GUIDESTAR.ORG.
